---
title: King Prawn Rigatoni with Creme Fraiche and Samphire
description: If you know our chefs, you'll know they love a prawn pasta dish. To be fair to them, who doesn't? We've added a sprinkling of samphire, a fabulous vegetable which grows along the coast and is sometimes called 'asparagus of the sea'. Enjoy!
